{"tid":1478592,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 大家小心, 呢兩日一定好多鬼","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T17:55:02.000Z","uid":56546,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"55fc0bd4ed9e3e5c8fa9830bf43c7f9eaa401a06","tid":1478592,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"小弟做關口<br />\n今日眼見成班解放軍咁嘅人已經分幾批<br />\n每次十幾人一齊過關口(好明顯有組織) <br />\n<br />\n同事們已經盡力釘咗好多個走<br />\n<br />\n但始終有藍絲同事會放行<br />\n同埋現實無可能ban曬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地成班入到黎嘅<br />\n已經秒速即刻返返大陸<br />\n<br />\n目的唔係今日黎搞事<br />\n可能係呢兩日經echannel入<br />\n或者方便未來隨時入黎<br />\n因為通行証只需要第一次成功入境<br />\n下次就可以自由用echannel入黎<br />\n<br />\n即係話黎緊經echannel, 同事再無能力再間佢係人係鬼<br />\n佢係一定黎到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知你地預咗有鬼, 可能諗住冷處理<br />\n但今次規模同平時唔同<br />\n<br />\n一定要有心理準備<br />\n同埋最好有方法去辦認自己人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我唔係要大家淆底唔敢出黎<br />\n相反更加要企出黎<br />\n依家呢個時勢已經等同鬥緊共產黨<br />\n你一縮只會落單被處理"},{"pid":"135a5f91122dc5bdc98aba7b6132482d16ffc115","tid":1478592,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"推佢老母"},{"pid":"2f24d922a3b0c70765f90445e5986960a3f60b03","tid":1478592,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ba9a565fdf118e84e7b0a2555a62b5979a9991","tid":1478592,"uid":16340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"影張証黎睇睇先"},{"pid":"d17b2baefe67f259c342c24686fb077b683f7326","tid":1478592,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6ba9a565fdf118e84e7b0a2555a62b5979a9991","tid":1478592,"uid":16340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"影張証黎睇睇先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪仲要質疑"